    "description": "Advantage Risk Management Co., Ltd. provides mental health management and disability support services in Japan. The company offers mental health management services, a support program that enhance mental health through stress checks, pulse surveys, training programs, counselling, etc.; health management support services related to health checkups; disability support services that develops group life-term disability insurance compensation; and operational support services. It also provides recruitment support services through aptitude tests; education support services through training programs; work-life balance support services that manages support for employees on leave due to maternity leave, childcare leave, personal injury, and illness; and industrial health systems. In addition, the company offers risk financing services, which consists of various insurance policies. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
